data.description:
BEAUTIFULLY REMODELED HOME NESTLED IN ON A CUL DE SAC IN THE GATED COMMUNITY OF TYMBER CREEK. 2.9%  ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE FOR QUALIFYING VETERANS.  THIS HOME IS ADORNED WITH  EXQUISITE FINISHES.  AS YOU ENTER YOUR NEW HOME YOU WILL BE GREETED BY THE WOOD LOOKING PORCELAIN TILES THAT FLOW THROUGHOUT THE LIVING AREA.  THE  SUNKEN LIVING ROOM FEATURES CATHEDRAL CEILINGS AND A MODERN STONE FIREPLACE.  THE KITCHEN THAT HAS BEEN TOTALLY UPDATED AND WILL BE THE CENTER FOR MANY GATHERINGS WITH A LARGE CENTER ISLAND THAT LEADS TO BOTH THE DINING AREA AND BREAKFAST NOOK.  THE KITCHEN IS PLENTIFUL WITH CABINET SPACE, FEATURES NEW APPLIANCES AND GRANITE COUNTER TOPS.  THE OWNERS BATH FEATURES A RAIN SHOWER WITH DETAILED FLOOR TO CEILING TILE WORK. THE DETAILS OF THE HOME CONTINUE WITH THE NEW AIR CONDITIONER AND VENTILATION DUCTS, NEW INSULATIONS, NEW GUTTERS, NEWS BLINDS AND EPOXY COATED GARAGE FLOOR.  THE YARD FEATURES A NEW 6 FOOT PRIVACY FENCE AND REBUILT DECK THAT IS PERFECT FOR RELAXING WITH FAMILY.  THE NEIGHBORHOOD FEATURES TREE LINED STREETS, POOL, CLUBHOUSE AND TENNIS FOR THE FAMILY TO ENJOY!  HAVE A BOAT OR RV TO PARK?  THE COMMUNITY ALSO HAS ADDITIONAL OPTIONAL PARKING FOR RECREATIONAL VEHICLES.  MAKE YOUR APPOINTMENT TODAY TO SEE YOUR NEW HOME!

Square footage received from tax rolls. All information recorded in the MLS intended to be accurate but cannot be guaranteed.
